{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I stay with them for a few years until everything cool off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And where was Mila?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mila was home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but she-- we have a little room-- kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One only-- kitchen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, we got in the-- in the building on Jozefinska 2, on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- then-- then, I found a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to the German Arbeitz, a work assigning place, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where was a Colonel Szepesi, Hungarian German, who was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was executed later on for helping the Jews by the SS in 1943, end of '43, for helping Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looks on my ID card and see on the ID card was written, Magister Leopold Pfefferberg, gymnasiallehrer, high school teacher.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He looks, and he said to me in German, dast ist kein beruf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is not a occupation-- gymnasial professor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't need any gymnasial professor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said, but I am a good mechanic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a good profession.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He erased this and put [GERMAN] a mechanic, polisher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, I was still-- every time I could get out, I was in the Schindler's or in the factory or his home till-- almost till the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he asked me many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always was dreaming that I have to get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How long I was with Mila, you understand, I was in because I have to protect her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I figure out when anything happen that we will be separated, I get out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I could thousand times get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No problem for me to get out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The day when there was ghetto liquidated, I was trying to get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
